      "raw_text": "Secretary l.. G. Monroe of the\nAlaska-Y ukon-Pacific exposition\ncommittee of Spokane county yes\nterday filed his final statement of\nexpenditures for the Spokane ex-\nhibit at the fair with the board of\ncounty commissioners. The report\ncovers a period of from May I, 1908,\nto January 26, 1910, and contains\nsome 500 items. The receipts and\nexpenditures balance evenly and\namounted to $10.233.S3"
